## 5. CSP Plant Output

```elixir
csp = EnergyX.Renewable.Solar.csp_plant_output(%{
  aperture_area_m2: 500_000, dni: 850, eta_collector: 0.73, eta_cycle: 0.38, parasitic_pct: 9.0
})

IO.puts("""
CSP Parabolic Trough Plant (500,000 m² aperture, DNI=850 W/m²):
  Thermal power:          #{csp.thermal_power_mw} MWth
  Gross electrical:       #{csp.gross_electric_mw} MWe
  Net electrical:         #{csp.net_electric_mw} MWe
  Solar-to-electric η:    #{Float.round(csp.solar_to_electric_efficiency * 100, 2)}%
""")
```

